please go to our Help Center to submit a ticket to apply for the "Add Ad Credits" feature first. Only account admin can add ad credits.

It looks like you need to submit a ticket to apply for the 'Add Ad Credits' feature. Only the account admin can add ad credits. You can do this by visiting our Help Center and submitting a request. If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!

To submit a ticket for the 'Add Ad Credits' feature, follow these steps:
1. Go to the NewsBreak Help Center: [NewsBreak Help Center](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/26538006900877-Advertising-Help-Center)
2. Sign in with your account credentials.
3. Click on 'Submit a request' at the top right corner of the page.
4. Fill out the form with the necessary details and mention that you need to apply for the 'Add Ad Credits' feature.
5. Submit the request.
If you have any issues or need further assistance, let me know!
